    "Therefore, future research needs to further identify the key factors affecting model output results and solve them systematically step by step.",
    "Fig. 17 In original conversation, it is evident that the is diarrhea with watery stools.",
    "Generally, in such cases, doctors would recommend oral rehydration with a saline solution to the patient to prevent dehydration.",
